 Keshia Thomas is an African-American woman known for a 1996 event at which she was photographed protecting a man believed to have been a Ku Klux Klan supporter. The resulting photograph, which was taken by Mark Brunner, has been considered to be iconic in nature and was named one of Life magazine's "Pictures of the Year" for 1996.

I cannot imagine having that level of goodness. She is a total badass.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/oNzpJSc</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[WiredIn2Much]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Told my brother I'm transgender...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/uJD8nQj</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/C2BNS4y.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/uJD8nQj</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Vylpes]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Have you ever?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/btrSAgQ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Hq2pcZu.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Seen a screenshot of a tweet on Imgur and go find said tweet on Twitter? Ya know, just to make sure it's real...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/b3YGAS5.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>...well I have, and I wasn't disappointed.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/btrSAgQ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[PeculiarPeanutButter]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I started out with a small million dollar loan</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/8YraUSQ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fpUzh2H.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xcy9wMM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/8YraUSQ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Flaptrapper]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>reduce urban sprawl</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/wl24ZVu</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LmhtU21.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/wl24ZVu</guid><